_sText:
This is my third map release. I just threw this together semi-randomly, like all of my maps. This one has sort of an "aztecish" feel to it, and should be good and even. This map has 32 player support, though i have not tried it with 32 bots, because my computer cant handle it, so I dont know if it will be too crowded.

This map is made for the Gun Game mod, but can really be used for straight Deathmatch aswell because i have included buyzones.

I have play tested it and it seemed to work fine, but if you have any issues, please let me know, so i can attempt to fix them.

Please provide *CONSTRUCTIVE* criticism.

ENJOY!
